---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Date Night Restaurants"
  description="Privacy policy for Date Night Restaurants. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when using our restaurant directory."
  canonical="https://datenightrestaurants.com/privacy/"
>
  <main class="legal-page">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> October 17, 2025</p>
      
      <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>We collect information you provide directly to us, such as when you create an account, make a reservation, or contact us for support.</p>
      
      <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Provide, maintain, and improve our services</li>
        <li>Process transactions and send related information</li>
        <li>Send technical notices, updates, security alerts, and support messages</li>
        <li>Respond to your comments, questions, and requests</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>3. Information Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
      <p>We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to third parties without your consent, except as described in this privacy policy.</p>
      
      <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
      <p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.</p>
      
      <h2>5. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
      <p>We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to collect and use personal information about you. You can control cookies through your browser settings.</p>
      
      <h2>6. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>We may use third-party services such as Google Analytics to analyze how users use our website. These services may use cookies and similar technologies.</p>
      
      <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal information. You may also opt out of certain communications from us.</p>
      
      <h2>8. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new privacy policy on this page.</p>
      
      <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at <a href="/contact/">our contact page</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    padding: 120px 0 80px;
    background: #FFF8F0;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }
  
  .container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }
  
  h1 {
    color: #3E2723;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  }
  
  h2 {
    color: #3E2723;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  }
  
  p {
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  ul {
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-left: 2rem;
  }
  
  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  strong {
    color: #3E2723;
  }
  
  a {
    color: #D2691E;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  
  a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
